Package: adMhLivingReview
Title: Living Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis of Atopic Dermatitis and
    Mental-Health Outcomes in Adults
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Review", "Team", email = "vishish123@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reproducible analysis pipeline for a PROSPERO-registered living
    systematic review of the association between atopic dermatitis and
    depression, anxiety, and suicidality / self-harm in adults. Uses metafor
    for random-effects meta-analysis, subgroup analysis, leave-one-out and
    influence diagnostics, Egger and trim-and-fill publication-bias checks,
    and a programmatic GRADE draft. Renders a Quarto site re-deployed monthly
    via GitHub Actions.
